This is the Perl module Class::Value::Net.

INSTALLATION

Class::Value::Net installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is
set up, you should just be able to do

    % cpan Class::Value::Net

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Class::Value::Net documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Class::Value::Net

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

